4:53:29Z,2026-06-20T04:54:00Z,0.00,0.00,results/00_infrastructure_gate/cuda_diagnostic_20260620T045329Z,\"Short diagnostic reproduced nvidia-smi exit 9 with CUDA-enabled PyTorch 2.12.0+cu130; PCI GPU and NVIDIA modules visible but PyTorch sees 0 CUDA devices; nvidia-modprobe did not repair; stop for operator-side VM restart/reboot and official Google GPU driver installer rerun.\"\n+infra_gate_20260620T050345Z,00_infrastructure_gate,blocked,cuda_preflight,roneneldan/TinyStories-3M,20260620,18cd0ebe6529a6b5fddcecad42eef2e6805cb0e5,,2026-06-20T05:03:45Z,2026-06-20T05:06:00Z,0.00,0.00,results/00_infrastructure_gate/infra_gate_20260620T050345Z,\"Fresh rerun stopped at mandated CUDA preflight: nvidia-smi exit 9; PCI GPU and NVIDIA modules visible but no /dev/nvidia0 or /dev/nvidiactl nodes observed; active /usr/bin/python3 lacks torch/transformers/datasets/devinterp/numpy/pandas; TinyStories loop, seq64/128 benchmarks, and sampler smoke not launched.\"\n+cuda_worker_diag_20260620T051003Z,00_infrastructure_gate,blocked,cuda_worker_diagnostic,roneneldan/TinyStories-3M,20260620,18cd0ebe6529a6b5fddcecad42eef2e6805cb0e5,,2026-06-20T05:10:03Z,2026-06-20T05:11:00Z,0.00,0.00,results/00_infrastructure_gate/cuda_worker_diag_20260620T051003Z,\"Diagnose-and-fix tick only: active /usr/bin/python3 lacks ML stack but .venv-bench-py311 has required packages and torch 2.12.0+cu130; nvidia-smi exit 9 persists, /dev/nvidia0 and /dev/nvidiactl absent, nvidia-modprobe exits 1; check_environment classifier updated and CPU smoke tests passed; no training/sampler launched.\"\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
